filesystem

Class DiskItemTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • filesystem.DiskItemTest

  • public class DiskItemTest
extends java.lang.Object
    A JUnit test class for testing the non-private methods of the DiskItem Class. The class is abstract, so we can use either one of the subclasses to test the interface of the superclass.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Tommy Messelis
